詹妮弗·安妮斯顿请求马修·佩里粉丝以新要求“尊重他的遗产” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jennifer-aniston-asks-matthew-perry-fans-to-honour-his-legacy-with-new-request-3550891?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jennifer-安妮斯顿要求马修·佩里的粉丝以新的请求来纪念他的遗产Liberty DunworthWed, 29 Nov 2023 17:13:35 +0000 NewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3550891 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·安妮斯顿和马修·佩里" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在她向这位演员表达了令人心碎的敬意之后，向粉丝们传达了这一信息</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jennifer-aniston-asks-matthew-perry-fans-to-honour-his-legacy-with-new-request-3550891">詹妮弗·安妮斯顿 (Jennifer Aniston) 请求马修·佩里 (Matthew Perry) 的粉丝“尊重他的遗产”，并提出了新的要求，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·安妮斯顿和马修·佩里" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>詹妮弗·安妮斯顿请求马修·佩里的粉丝支持他内心深处的事业，帮助“尊重他的遗产”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/friends-the-reunion-best-moments-2950054">《老友记：重聚》：最美好的时刻——以及它们会让你感觉自己多大了</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位因在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>《老友记》</em></a>中饰演钱德勒·宾而闻名的演员上个月被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-dead-54-friends-tributes-3524335">发现死于洛杉矶的家中</a>，享年 54 岁，并于 11 月初<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/friends-stars-attend-funeral-of-matthew-perry-3530457">举行了私人葬礼</a>。</p><p>在他去世的消息传出后，该剧的合作演员们向佩里表达了一系列衷心的敬意。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jennifer-aniston-pays-tribute-to-matthew-perry-this-one-has-cut-deep-3540177">詹妮弗·安妮斯顿（Jennifer Aniston）的情感信息</a>，她在该剧中扮演了雷切尔·格林（Rachel Green）的角色，并写道，这种损失已经“深深影响”，并引发了“我以前从未经历过的疯狂情绪浪潮”。</p><p>现在，安妮斯顿呼吁她的数百万社交媒体粉丝通过支持他的基金会来帮助以新的方式记住这位演员。</p><p>该项目名为<a href="https://matthewperryfoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“马修·佩里基金会”</a> ，旨在提高人们对毒瘾的认识，并旨在强调“马修对帮助他人的持久承诺”。</p><p>该网站写道：“它将尊重他的遗产，并以他自己的话语和经历为指导，并以他为尽可能多的人的生活带来改变的热情为动力。”它还分享了佩里的一句话，其中写道：“当我去世时，我不希望<em>朋友</em>成为第一个提到的事情——我希望帮助别人成为第一个提到的事情。我将用我的余生来证明这一点。上瘾的力量太强大，任何人都无法独自克服。但只要齐心协力，一天一天，我们就能战胜它。” </p><figure id="attachment_3550898" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3550898" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3550898" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry1@2000x1270.jpg" alt="马修·佩里和詹妮弗·安妮斯顿 1998 年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry1@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry1@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry1@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry1@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry1@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jennifer-Aniston-Matthew-Perry1@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3550898" class="wp-caption-text">马修·佩里和詹妮弗·安妮斯顿，1998 年。图片来源：Vinnie Zuffante/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/jenniferaniston/3246295516027234666/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">安妮斯顿分享了基金会页面的链接，还写了一个标题</a>，上面写着：“在#GivingTuesday，请与我和马蒂的家人一起支持他的基金会——该基金会正在努力帮助那些患有毒瘾的人……”他会很感激这份爱”。</p><p>佩里对这项事业的承诺部分来自于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-gives-advice-in-last-interview-before-death-3525108">他自己与止痛药成瘾和酗酒的斗争</a>，他在回忆录《<em>朋友、情人和可怕的大事》</em>中诚实地讨论了这些问题。在书中，他还讲述了这些挣扎如何影响他在情景喜剧中的时间，并告诉<em>《早安美国》</em> ，他希望他的故事能够帮助人们。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://matthewperryfoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>了解有关马修·佩里基金会的更多信息。</p><p>除了安妮斯顿之外，其他联合主演也向佩里表达了敬意。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-schwimmer-pays-tribute-to-matthew-perry-i-will-never-forget-your-impeccable-comic-timing-3540206">在该剧中扮演罗斯·盖勒的大卫·施维默回忆起这位演员“无可挑剔的喜剧时机”和宽广的“心”</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/lisa-kudrow-pays-tribute-matthew-perry-3540344">扮演菲比·布菲的丽莎·库卓则写道：“谢谢你在身体不好的时候出现在工作岗位上。”</a>然后，变得非常聪明。感谢你给了一个人最美好的十年。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzrZeG5P0n6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3p